cc:Work.dc:title: Hot Dog with sausage, bun and mustard
cc:Work.dc:description:
A colored line-drawing of a hotdog with sausage, bun and mustard.
The original by SRD has open ended paths, making it hard to color. Completed the paths and added gradient colors for a more realistic hot dog feel.
Used for our Patriotic Sausage BBQ Hotdog T-Shirt: https://bzh314.com/shop/food/Sausage/
